name: Parallel Universe Planet Project #0
description:
Parallel Universe Planet Project #0

Parallel Universe Planet Project is a series of interactive artwork projects for P5JS. Each planet has its own unique physical rules.

Planet #0 is a planet of information, with many consciousnesses, data, and algorithms surrounding the gravity field. Color does not exist on this planet. When the viewer clicks the mouse or touches the phone screen, the gravity structure of the planet can be changed.

P.S. For those who collect "Horizon-sea", "Sphere-sun" or "Vertical-forest",  they will let the Earth's landscape change the aesthetic experience of planet #0 by displaying the relevant data images and colors.
